{"tid":423351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「真人版赤木晴子」竟然人在中國","createTime":"2017-10-03T23:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T02:28:04.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a508b87b23bf9839bda461bd63460543f2a4bd82","tid":423351,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T23:51:07.000Z","msg":"日本漫畫《男兒當入樽》紅極一時，女主角赤木晴子更是吸引了不少宅男，而被稱為「中國最美籃球女裁判」的亓（音其）浩，近日被網民封為「真人版赤木晴子」，在網上走紅！<br />\n<br />\n不過，原來亓浩是一名中國大學生籃球聯賽（CUBA）球員，裁判只是「客串」，當日「因為幫朋友的忙，所以去參加了這次比賽的吹罰」。變成網上紅人後，讓她有一點困擾，亓浩稱，她的身份仍是球員，直言不想當網紅，亦不想把自己的私生活曝光。<br />\n<br />\n亓浩從小學開始打籃球，她所在的小學女子籃球隊是湖南省第一名，之後一直有持續打籃球，目前她在湖南師範大學資源與環境科學學院就讀，而其隊伍一直都是CUBA中的強隊，常年保持着湖南省第一，也打出過全國前四的好成績。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/075044_e8dc71b8f57f3f2492da598b4a662e35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F075044_e8dc71b8f57f3f2492da598b4a662e35.jpg&h=5b4c44b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/075045_23e0bdfc1c68a8b6ba06a319eb913bc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F075045_23e0bdfc1c68a8b6ba06a319eb913bc9.jpg&h=13f7c04c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/075046_c19031efb09fc9adae2f087ae6cac8df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F075046_c19031efb09fc9adae2f087ae6cac8df.jpg&h=b55a1d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/075046_6a7272f67dbb3bfb79e01af12c5d39d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F075046_6a7272f67dbb3bfb79e01af12c5d39d5.jpg&h=c09d04ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d52b0ffb5eca3dede0d2596d4c8cb72f37e3a46c","tid":423351,"uid":132038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:07:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b029e174b9305dd7a84288ed9058d6c63b2c771","tid":423351,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:08:25.000Z","msg":"新聞真易寫<br />\n打藍球嘅女就係晴子.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520d503f416c53563a6d76c3659373f515d87995","tid":423351,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:12:32.000Z","msg":"屌第三張成個阿嬸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5898278e6a56b57cf7def24b6cc9b8ed24c3421","tid":423351,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:13:07.000Z","msg":"又咪俾領導安西教練啪啪啪"},{"pid":"bbc7f65c14149e5206c8d9726f66161a72922009","tid":423351,"uid":130141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"打籃球點解仲咁白淨？"},{"pid":"f7fc4fe3c0effea73edadd58d6e54421b87d3edc","tid":423351,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打籃球點解仲咁白淨？</blockquote><br />\n窮人先打街場<br />\n佢係職業球員打開體育館"},{"pid":"7904438369a55ada6022d6f7db7fd09134b7c728","tid":423351,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:51:39.000Z","msg":"真係好撚白淨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f072a4f63b7665b548f9d8d928d15d873605ad15","tid":423351,"uid":150294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:53:08.000Z","msg":"白淨泥味輕磚！"},{"pid":"d1a35f0b845db38f8dcd8785c20fae7bf35fee9f","tid":423351,"uid":139349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 赤木剛憲就似"},{"pid":"320064604d7563d39b84050188b40aee3d06954a","tid":423351,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:34:34.000Z","msg":"男人腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm